Usage: ON [#|+|-|^|&|@]KICK [-|^]<parameters> [action]
  This is activated whenever someone kicks someone else from a
  channel.  The parameters for the action are as follows:
    $0    nickname of person who kicked
    $1    the nickname of the person being kicked
    $2    the channel the person is being kicked from
    $3-   the kick comment
